          "date": "2025-08-06 21:30:42.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-19241 o2iblnd: clean up conn on CM address change",
        "message": "LU-19241 o2iblnd: clean up conn on CM address change\n\nIn RoCEv2 bonding scenario, link failover causes\nRDMA_CM_EVENT_ADDR_CHANGE event. If connection is not\ncleaned up at this point, it gets stuck and prevents\nclean module unload.\n\nDisconnect on RDMA_CM_EVENT_ADDR_CHANGE.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=sanity-lnet\nSigned-off-by: Serguei Smirnov <ssmirnov@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I065732bd7dbfcf6584bbec7aa6f8a09a166c3c16\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
